{"tid":1525101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地地鐵站First-aider被拒事件經過","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:15:21.000Z","uid":211021,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9585665e795dba775e3bcc41e192fcd90d42199b","tid":1525101,"uid":211021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"我係畫面中其中一個急救員，我地約喺2320時收到消息，油麻地地鐵站內有急救員被捕，及有四名傷者急需護理，卻於2330時於到達油麻地地鐵站內時，被一名反黑組探員以粗暴語氣要求離開，在場的兩名女記者甚至被拍打鏡頭及被其以警棍恐嚇，並要求所有人包括記者離開否則會作出拘捕，但卻完全沒有回應是否有傷者或是否已送院<br />\n<br />\n本人與當場的其他急救人員都持有有效成人急救證書，或是護士註冊證，即使聖約翰救護車到場，但亦都未準許進入站内救援，直至一個小時後，才有防暴警察表示所有傷者已送院"},{"pid":"46eed086b01fb6b89a6f9ca7463aa229f12a2381","tid":1525101,"uid":247198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:41:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbe81859f90581f5efa38e09b38cdfb0660f989a","tid":1525101,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死黑警"},{"pid":"e6c29124d818b8160a4240b18e275bacdd7b71a1","tid":1525101,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:42:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e767fb622b779ca1e9a57e2a0ee8aae8c6a35cc7","tid":1525101,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:42:59.000Z","msg":"Retweet<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/YanWa369/status/1167871387525992448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYanWa369%2Fstatus%2F1167871387525992448&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=3369029f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYanWa369%2Fstatus%2F1167871387525992448&h=e1751fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/YanWa369/status/1167871387525992448</a>"},{"pid":"96a7bad76322933130b18cafa